    "title": "违反国家行政法规禁止销售的商品及服务实施细则",
    "followRuleId": "1287356202036105216",
    "content": "<h1 style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.11</span></strong><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">违反国家行政法规禁止销售的商品及服务</span></strong></h1>\n<h2 style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.11.1</span></strong><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">涉嫌违反《中华人民共和国文物保护法》等相关规定的文物：</span></strong></h2>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">背景：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">涉嫌违反《中华人民共和国文物保护法》等相关规定的文物：请遵守《中华人民共和国刑法》、《中华人民共和国文物保护法》等相关法律法规的规定。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">规则定义：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">写明出土地和出土时间的文物，如1969年出土于甘肃省某墓中的马踏飞燕等。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">标准：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">平台禁止发布上述文物类商品。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">常见问题：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1）文物和收藏品都是禁止发布的吗？</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">不是的，文物是不允许买卖的，但收藏品不受限制。如果是文物，即使声明用于收藏，仍然是不允许发布的。</span></p>\n<h2 style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.11.2</span></strong><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">烟草专卖品、烟草专用机械、电子烟及相关配件：</span></strong></h2>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">背景：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">请遵守《中华人民共和国烟草专卖法》、《严厉打击利用互联网等信息网络非法经营烟草专卖品的通告》、《关于进一步保护未成年人免受电子烟侵害的通告》、《电子烟管理办法》等相关法律法规的规定。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">规则定义：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">烟草、雪茄、电子烟类制品，包括但不限于加热不燃烧型、烟油型电子烟及雾化型电子烟等；卷烟纸、滤嘴棒、烟用丝束，以及将烟丝和烟纸加工成成品烟的烟草专用机械；电子烟配件类商品；茶烟、花烟等类烟产品。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">标准：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">平台禁止发布烟草专卖品，如卷烟及相关配件、专用卷烟设备、雪茄、电子烟等，请勿销售上述商品，或使用变形、暗语等形式私下销售。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">案例：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><img class=\"wscnph\" style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border-style: none; word-break: break-all;\" src=\"https://img30.360buyimg.com/venderrule//jfs/t1/330894/35/13552/32504/68c7cfe8F54d1f595/4268410d1dd259ae.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">温馨提示：如您发布的商品被误拦截，请联系客服通知相关人员进行系统优化。</span></p>\n<h2 style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.11.3</span></strong><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">公章：</span></strong></h2>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">背景：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">企业刻制公章，需凭相关资质证照到本单位所在地县级以上公安机关办理刻制印章通知单或介绍信，然后凭着通知单或介绍信，到公安机关指定的刻字厂或刻字店刻制，不可直接售卖，请不要在京东上发布。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">规则定义：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">财务章、合同章及银行的转帐章、现金收讫章、现金付讫章等。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">标准：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">平台禁止发布上述企业公章类商品或提供此类刻章服务。</span></p>\n<h2 style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.11.4</span></strong><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">涉及网络账号类买卖服务：</span></strong></h2>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">背景：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">互联网用户账号密码在卖家手里可随时找回，极易引发交易及后续用户使用风险。网盘账号类因网盘内所储存的内容存在涉黄、盗版侵权等风险。另外，以支付、社交、媒体为主要功能的互联网用户账号类与用户个人隐私、言论存在较高关联，请不要发布。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">规则定义：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">出售、购买、交换或以任何形式交易网络实名账号（包括但不限于社交媒体账号、游戏账号、平台账号等）</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">标准：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">平台禁止发布上述网络账号类商品。</span></p>\n<h2 style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.11.5</span></strong><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">其他相关法规禁止发布或存在风险的商品及服务：</span></strong></h2>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">规则定义：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">包括但不限于</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①根据国家相关法规禁止销售、发布的商品及服务，包括但不限于胎儿性别鉴定、代挂号服务、挂靠代缴社保等。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">②根据地方