 style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家的行为，发生在本规则生效之日以前的，适用当时的规则。发生在本规则生效之日以后的，适用本规则。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: white; text-align: left; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东可根据运营情况随时调整本规则并以公告的形式向商家公示。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: white; text-align: left; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3.</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-se